{"tid":1900720,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"消息指今晚佛堂再多一宗初步確診  若最終確診將取代「打邊爐家族」成最大族群","createTime":"2020-02-27T11:26:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T12:14:48.000Z","uid":212626,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d9cf0fc8be426faedea2a2c17a11ff812c3ae421","tid":1900720,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T11:26:25.000Z","msg":"武漢新型冠狀病毒在港肆虐，有政府消息人士向《立場新聞》透露，本港再新增1宗初步確診個案，病人是1名89歲女性，報稱曾到過北角美輪大廈「福慧精舍」。<br />\n<br />\n政府消息人士表示，病人曾到柏立基夫人普通科門診診所求醫，地址位於北角七姊妹道140號1樓，病人因有病徵，回家翌日早上透過樣本瓶自行採取深嗟液樣本，交回門診診所後轉交衞生署進行快速測試。<br />\n<br />\n若該89歲女病人最終確診，確診個案將會增至93宗，與「佛堂群組」有關的個案亦會增至14宗。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/武漢肺炎-消息指福慧精舍再多一宗初步確診-經普通科門診採口水樣本/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E6%8C%87%E7%A6%8F%E6%85%A7%E7%B2%BE%E8%88%8D%E5%86%8D%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%97%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E7%B6%93%E6%99%AE%E9%80%9A%E7%A7%91%E9%96%80%E8%A8%BA%E6%8E%A1%E5%8F%A3%E6%B0%B4%E6%A8%A3%E6%9C%AC%2F&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKwg2XwNgY6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=2b8a75ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E6%8C%87%E7%A6%8F%E6%85%A7%E7%B2%BE%E8%88%8D%E5%86%8D%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%97%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E7%B6%93%E6%99%AE%E9%80%9A%E7%A7%91%E9%96%80%E8%A8%BA%E6%8E%A1%E5%8F%A3%E6%B0%B4%E6%A8%A3%E6%9C%AC%2F&h=d69ca3b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/武漢肺炎-消息指福慧精舍再多一宗初步確診-經普通科門診採口水樣本/</a>"},{"pid":"07b6237a1add7466ef764e63cd7db7a39caed3f6","tid":1900720,"uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T11:27:20.000Z","msg":"打邊爐家族總共有13人確診<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0392898b17e739783d25a07b362ec2ddbd0956bf","tid":1900720,"uid":301707,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"reply